data.description: 4 Bedroom 3 Bath Split Foyer Home In a Great Neighborhood. This Home offers an Open Floor Plan with an Updated Kitchen with Stainless Steel  Appliances. The Home has Vinyl Plank Flooring and Tile Throughout. The Main Level offers 3 Bedrooms and 2 Full Baths. The Downstairs has another Huge Bedroom and a Large Living room and Bathroom. The Laundry room is also on the Lower Level. The Back Yard is Fenced in with an Inground Pool that is 8 Feet Deep on one end with a New Pool Liner. The Home also offers a 2 Car Garage. The Home has a Large Back Deck, that is Perfect for Entertaining..
